[CENTER][SIZE=6][B]Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra Accessories Guide[/B][/SIZE][/CENTER]

[B]Welcome to the comprehensive accessories guide for the Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra![/B]

This guide covers cases, screen protectors, chargers, and more - all with verified purchase links and up-to-date pricing.

[B]Device Highlights:[/B]
• S Pen silo built-in (critical for case design)
• No native Qi2 magnets (requires magnetic cases for MagSafe)
• 45W USB-PD PPS wired charging
• Flat 6.9" display (easier for screen protectors)
• Titanium frame
• Ultrasonic fingerprint sensor

[B]Charging:[/B]
• Wired: 45W USB-PD PPS
• Wireless: 15W Qi (no native magnets)

